===========================================
yashiro: A template CLI tool based on jinja
===========================================

.. image:: https://github.com/spapanik/yashiro/actions/workflows/build.yml/badge.svg
  :alt: Build
  :target: https://github.com/spapanik/yashiro/actions/workflows/build.yml
